It is OK. Arrived quickly.

The problem with this action pack is that these movies do not stand the test of time. This means that you are interested in reliving the 80's and 90's or you have an interest in studying that time period. If you are a Chuck Norris fan then you will enjoy this pack with 3 of his films. There is also a sprinkle of well known actors, Jackie Chan, Dolph Lungren and Charlie Sheen in some of their earliest films. So if you are a movie historian of sorts you now have another reason to get this pack. Or you need to be an action film junkie that is willing to try action movies that lack all of the modern technology such as computer graphic imagining. The storylines cover a wide range of topics such as bringing down drug lords, the Kennedy assassination, Terrorist on US soil, Revenge for the death of an FBI agents wife, etc. If the price is right and you want 15 hours that will take you back in time on an action ride, guns, hand to hand combat, car chases, then this may be for you.
I enjoy ordering items that can and will be a blessing to others.  I am for sure that every person will enjoy a small gift of appreication.
Since I did not view the movies personally, I am only stating what my son said about them.  He said they were good, and he is not subject to hyperbole, so I assume they met his expectations.
Some of these movies were OK and some were old movies. Most are B movies, but a fair value if you want to add to your collection.
